title: You Are Equipped | Joel Osteen
itunes:title: You Are Equipped | Joel Osteen
description:
You have everything you need to live a life of victory. When God created you, He anointed you with the creativity, talent and ideas to accomplish everything He's called you to do. 

Your best days are still ahead, and together we can make a difference in this world with the message of God's hope and love.

To give visit JoelOsteen.com/GiveHope
